Arsenal have been handed a welcome draw against Slavia Prague in the Europa League quarter-finals, with Manchester United to face newcomers Granada. The quarter-final first legs will be played on April 8 with the second legs on April 15. Europa League quarter-final draw Granada vs Manchester United Arsenal vs Slavia Prague Ajax vs Roma Dinamo Zagreb vs Villarreal Europa League semi-final draw Granada vs Manchester United/Ajax vs Roma Dinamo Zagreb/Villarreal vs Arsenal/Slavia Prague 